  <summary date="2017-03-08T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">National Criminal Justice Commission Act of 2017

This bill establishes the National Criminal Justice Commission to conduct a comprehensive review of the criminal justice system; make recommendations for criminal justice reform; and disseminate findings and guidance to the federal government and to state, local, and tribal governments.</summary>
